outputs.output_descr:
The project aims at strengthening the information system related to violations on children and adolescents rights, through activities targeted to the dissemination of its effective use by all Brazilian states and municipalities. 
The processes and products generated will provide:
1) Data management and information on violations / situations of the rights of children and adolescents (providing the framework and objective analysis of situations of rape, following the appropriate referrals in order to guarantee rights);
2) Monitoring and evaluation of public policies warranty rights at the local, state and federal grounds (featuring statistics that allow you to view the panorama of the city and state regarding the rights of children and adolescents;
3) Mobilization network and social control in favor of guaranteed rights (such as encouraging the adoption of protective measures and analysis of the local situation);
4) Production of scenario and situation reports on ensuring rights of children and adolescents in Brazil, in order to subsidize management policy in the national level and prepare reports of international commitments of the Brazilian State on the subject.
